The first thing I am doing to learn GitHub is watch a YouTube Video "1.1: Introduction - Git and GitHub for Poets" at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BCQHnlnPusY&feature=youtu.be.

Keywords:
Repository:  A Folder for your proeject.
Commit:       Save the file.


How-To:
How To Edit a file on :   Click on the file to bring it to the forefront.  Then click on the pen icon on the top right of the edit frame. Now youre file is in edit mode.  You can edit the file.
